<section id="process" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="badge">Four-Step Process</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">A process built for durable growth, not rushed installs.</h2>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <article class="card process-step"><span>1</span><h3>Assess & Prepare</h3><p>Evaluate grade, drainage, and soil condition before any seed is applied.</p></article>
      <article class="card process-step"><span>2</span><h3>Grade & Seed</h3><p>Correct surface issues and apply the right seed strategy for site conditions.</p></article>
      <article class="card process-step"><span>3</span><h3>Hydromulch & Protect</h3><p>Lock seed to soil using mulch coverage that helps reduce washout risk.</p></article>
      <article class="card process-step"><span>4</span><h3>Water, Grow & Maintain</h3><p>Provide clear watering guidance and maintenance support during establishment.</p></article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
